(1499, 1, '2016-04-20 09:10:47', '2016-04-20 16:10:47', '<p class="caps">Hey, maybe i will give you a call sometime. your number still 911? i just heard about evans new position,good luck to you evan backstabber, bastard, i mean baxter. good morning, oh in case i don''t see you, good afternoon, good evening and goodnight. look at that, it''s exactly three seconds before i honk your nose and pull your underwear over your head. brain freeze. excuse me, i''d like to ass you a few questions. we got no food we got no money and our pets heads are falling off! haaaaaaarry. good morning, oh in case i don''t see you, good afternoon, good evening and goodnight. look ma i''m road kill look ma i''m road kill we got no food we got no money and our pets heads are falling off! haaaaaaarry. your entrance was good, his was better.</p>\r\n<p class="caps">Alrighty then kinda hot in these rhinos. i just heard about evans new position,good luck to you evan backstabber, bastard, i mean baxter. look at that, it''s exactly three seconds before i honk your nose and pull your underwear over your head. here she comes to wreck the day. we''re going for a ride on the information super highway. it''s because i''m green isn''t it! kinda hot in these rhinos. your entrance was good, his was better. alrighty then brain freeze. excuse me, i''d like to ass you a few questions.</p>', 'Jim', 'The funniest or stupidest?', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jim', '', '', '2016-04-21 10:01:06', '2016-04-21 17:01:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost/maxBel-wp/in-class/?post_type=product&#038;p=1499', 0, 'product', '', 0),
